article_title: These clean-energy stocks including Tesla could benefit from a Biden win, says Baird
article_text: (This story is for CNBC PRO subscribers only.)With the election just about one month away, and with the first presidential debate behind us, Baird looked at how the names in its energy technology and resource management groups might perform under President Donald Trump versus former Vice President Joe Biden. The election’s outcome may be far from certain, but Baird said to expect volatility either way.
